reviewText: It's funny how I used to watch this show when I went to college. I just had to see Kaitlin, I ain't gonna lie! Okay, I can't count out Ryan Steele, or JB Reese. Those guys could kick some Skug butt!! It was a trip to see the daily adventures of the heroes of Cross World City repeatedly defeating the evil industrialist Carl Ziktor/Grimlord. I can't wait to complete my VR Troopers collection when the remaining half of season two is finally released. I love Shout! factory! They are my heroes!
Title: VR Troopers: Season 2, Vol. 1
